<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">sudo ap=
t install python3-pip -y
pip3 install flask</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"af9f49fc5ac4">Modify app:</p>
