<h2 local-id=3D"051475274ad0" id=3D"Task18-TechnicalDocument-Step9:RequestA=
CMSSLCertificate">Step 9: Request ACM SSL Certificate</h2>
<p local-id=3D"4f626bbb07b1">Navigate to AWS Certificate Manager =E2=86=92 =
Request a certificate =E2=86=92 Request a public certificate:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d0ee5a589ce2">Add domain names: site3.karna.pushkar.cloud an=
d site4.karna.pushkar.cloud</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"490b511187c5">Validation method: DNS validation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"2b8e18a441c8">Click Create records in Route 53 to auto-creat=
e the CNAME validation records</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"c46b24e251ca">Wait for certificate status to change to Issue=
d (typically 1=E2=80=935 minutes with Route 53 DNS validation).</p>
<p local-id=3D"8ab9413067a7">Navigate to the ALB =E2=86=92 Listeners =E2=86=
=92 Add listener:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"fa932a8239c0">Protocol: HTTPS</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3161e53e4bc3">Port: 443</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"074e9c7fd3f8">SSL Certificate: select the ACM certificate is=
sued in the previous step</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0e1eb66e6400">Default action: Forward to flask-target-group<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b430d01f39b5">Optionally add a redirect rule on the HTTP:80 =
listener to redirect all traffic to HTTPS:443.</p><span class=3D"confluence=
